{
  "stem": "11723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the heads of the congregation wanted to keep calm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody keep calm, this, too, shall pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most people didn't think very much as to what they were going to do, until March 19 of 1944, when the Germans finally came into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they just occupied the country [SNAPS] overnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that point, every Jew had to start wearing a yellow star on the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] left-hand side, 10 centimeters in diameter, and-- except children under the age of six.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I never wore a star, because I was under the age of six.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my parents did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would like to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dispel the notion that the Hungarians just were oppressed, and because the Germans were there, that was the only reason they persecuted Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarians were just as vicious, if not more vicious, than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Much more vicious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to tell you how vicious they were, I'll give you two incidents, one in which I was present as a child, and I remember, and one where my-- my father was present.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or rather, my father's experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was going on the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was coming and going-- he was very brave-- without-- without the star.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And If you wore the-- if you didn't wear the star, it was punishable by even death, depending on who your judge was, not that there was a court of law, but, I mean, dependent on who caught you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father was going somewhere in Budapest, and all of a sudden, somebody yells at him, oh, now I got you, Armin!",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he happened to have been a disgruntled employee who was fired because he was stealing.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
